    endAlt: "Cable Rear Delt Fly ending position: an athletic adult using cable attachment. Arms pulled apart and back, hands at shoulder level. Rear delts and upper back fully contracted. Cables crossed, arms in a wide-open position. Emphasis falls on the shoulders with assistance from back and traps.",
